reviewText: I am a fan of all the Red Shoe Diaries Movies. This was good!
Absolutely Love the Series and Excellent reproduction of the original Tapes.

If you like erotic movies, theres no one better than Zalman King. His RedShoeDiaries movies have been out since the 80's. They never go out of style. I am not into watching pornographic movies but I do like at times a light erotica with a story and some classiness about it. Theres a good one starring Billy Zane that I recommend. And the pilot is really good too. If you like a lightly spiced  erotica "RedShoeDiaries" is the way to go.
